item.title: Script getting stuck at bank
item.dc:creator: @junior junior
item.description:
@junior wrote:

Then make your own bank screen function and replace it over SRL’s. For example…
[php]
function BankScreen: boolean;
begin
if (GetColor(x, y) = 000000) then
Result := True;
end;
[/php]
Get color is simple and probably will work, try that out.
